B.Bn=new A.iE("P0301","Cylinder 1 misfire detected",B.Bm,"Cylinder 1 isn't firing reliably. You may feel shaking at idle or hesitation when accelerating. Unburned fuel can overheat and ruin the catalytic converter, so this one shouldn't wait.",B.Er,"Start with the spark plug and coil on cylinder 1 \u2014 a shop will often swap the coil with another cylinder to confirm.","$75\u2013$400 typical (plug/coil) \xb7 up to $1,500 if injector")
